snippet.title: Dreaming Dino!
snippet.description:
Dino's neck was unusually short among the dinosaurs.
While sleeping, Dino ends up getting the long neck he’s longed for in his dream…

App Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/id1527726706

Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.super_toki.giraffe

#likeadino #likedino #dino #toki #supertoki
